OL,11,Fprovided by Bolton Council after the   
OL,12,Fman was discharged from hospital.      
OL,14,FThese included carers not turning up   
OL,15,Fand carers not getting help quickly    
OL,16,Fwhen he did not answer the door. He    
OL,17,Flater died.                            
